{"tid":1280443,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔衝既可以點支援呢","createTime":"2019-07-03T03:35:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T06:34:58.000Z","uid":228244,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a10f4a782f08d9f9af0143531bdd4fe5ed5b00bd","tid":1280443,"uid":228244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:35:34.000Z","msg":"不如大家討論吓。7.1見到嚟後生撤退時連八達通都唔敢用，咁夜著住黑衫好易被狗咬，如果冇力衝既人，可以點樣在後線支援，令佢哋安全撤退? brainstorm 吓"},{"pid":"e2479d69a10563cacc145be9380918ae59c2d0b5","tid":1280443,"uid":242672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:40:34.000Z","msg":"戰線附近探路，幫手搵撤退路線"},{"pid":"5be1d424023e855565cc1797d0ad1db7cf30c59c","tid":1280443,"uid":60057,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T03:52:01.000Z","msg":"如果冇事冇幹出街用八達通呀留記錄呀，咁警察都搞唔到你既。<br />\n發夢咁諗，唔衝既去現場打掩護有冇得諗?<br />\n幾十萬人既八達通記錄，原來個個都去海富食早餐，去PP SHOPPING，入邊D CCTV影低晒大家行街睇戲食飯，警察點敢搞你"},{"pid":"244b1abbdd367a958bebbd6c6c0bc9464778f54f","tid":1280443,"uid":108687,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T04:03:58.000Z","msg":"#1 問嘅方向都好清楚<br />\n<br />\n即時諗到嘅係提供義載，但係諗深一層風險過高，會畀藍絲同警察混入。務必警戒。<br />\n<br />\n現時最有效嘅做法係好似當晚咁，走入循道衛理堂暫避。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大方向係：增加搜捕難度。e.g. 衣物、鞋、背囊(以後應該長期遮掩背囊款色或設機制交換背囊，令行動者不能辨認)。e.g. 遮敞、破壞監視鏡頭"},{"pid":"1b9fa608809c7fa30ad73419b04146b2a6100b92","tid":1280443,"uid":108687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:33:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2528022960565882&amp;id=1629975780370609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2528022960565882%26id%3D1629975780370609&d=ItsvLBlInL5d1alZeSWtsBVFNPQ3ENA2ZLNhq8Q56nc%3D&h=f49e2931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2528022960565882&amp;id=1629975780370609</a>"},{"pid":"34bb1b2b9255b2643a093039419003b95ccf14f5","tid":1280443,"uid":263778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T06:34:58.000Z","msg":"（方向整理）唔好比社運停落黎！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1280795\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1280795</a>"}]}